Suspected anthrax hoaxer arrested
---------------------------------
Clayton Lee Waagner, the suspected author of hoax letters sent to abortion
clinics that claimed to be contaminated with anthrax, was arrested
Wednesday after eluding authorities for months, according to federal
authorities.

